are  subject  to  the  Age  60  Rule,  Part  135  is  not.  There’s  no  limit 
at  all  on  being  a  commercial  pilot  in  Part  135.  Now,  they’re  flying 
to  the  same  places,  along  comes  the  FAA  and  says,  ‘‘We  want  you 

