erybody wants to hear you. 

Senator  BURNS.  You  might  want  to  pull  that  microphone  up,  ev-

Mr.  EICHELKRAUT.  Thank  you  for  the  opportunity  to  testify  on 
the  Age  60  Rule.  Mr.  Chairman,  I  commend  you  and  Chairman 
